<ul style="float:right;list-style:none; margin-top: 20px; margin-right: 20px; font-size: 175%;">
<li style="display: inline-block; margin-left: 40px; padding:20px 0px;">
<a class="main-nav1"href="https://www.geos.ed.ac.uk/~s2259785/home.html" style="text-decoration:none;">Home</a>
</li>
